<subSubSection pageId="74" pageNumber="558" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="74.[1451,2660,1034,2203]" pageId="74" pageNumber="558">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1453,1799,2014,2047]" pageId="74" pageNumber="558">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. Kalko’s Yellow-eared Batis rare and restricted to a few locations in 
<collectingRegion box="[2003,2211,2053,2086]" country="Panama" name="Bocas del Toro" pageId="74" pageNumber="558">Bocas del Toro</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[2226,2341,2053,2086]" name="Panama" pageId="74" pageNumber="558">Panama</collectingCountry>
. It has not been found in the wild since the late 1970s and could be extinct.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
